How's the stick doin?  Are you finding it's shield effect as useful as you thought (or Verant thought) it would be?  I have mixed feelings on the subject.  I was actually thinking a lot about it on the way to work today.  In my eyes, if you play your wizard correctly, you don't get beat upon.  But there had to be a reason they put this on an epic item.  Perhaps Verant's vision is that our true destructive nature is hidden in our AE's  (well.. it's not that hidden.  We are damage god's in this form of playing.)  But being that there isn't a majority of wizards that have gotten the hang of AE fighting, perhaps this is Verant's way of telling us to use them more.  *shrug* just something to think about.<br>
